short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows the automatic migration of content from OnlyFans to iFans.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Migration tool to import data from OnlyFans to iFans. Users can import their existed posts and media. It's useful for users to not create the same posts twice if they are using both of this sites. Only authorized users can migrate their content, so it's safety to other user's content.
